Foreign buyers will be charged a higher stamp fee for buying real estate in the UK
Foreign buyers will incur a higher stamp fee for buying real estate in the UK, while the extra funds will be used to help the homeless, according to the Tories' new plans
The measure will counteract the success of Corbin's campaign to attract young voters
